SYNQDRIVE PHASE 3 AUTH & RBAC

Purpose:
Design authentication and authorization model.

------------------------------------------------
AUTHENTICATION
------------------------------------------------

Authentication confirms identity.

Possible providers:
- Clerk
- custom auth

Users table stores:

id
email
name
auth_provider_id
status

------------------------------------------------
AUTHORIZATION MODEL
------------------------------------------------

Access is determined by:

1 identity
2 organization membership
3 role
4 product licensing
5 optional station scope

------------------------------------------------
ROLES
------------------------------------------------

Master Admin
Org Admin
Sub Admin
Worker
Driver
Customer

------------------------------------------------
MASTER ADMIN
------------------------------------------------

Platform level access.

Capabilities:
- manage organizations
- manage users
- configure DIMO
- configure Stripe
- manage product licensing
- access prospects database

------------------------------------------------
ORG ADMIN
------------------------------------------------

Full control inside an organization.

Capabilities:
- manage users
- manage stations
- manage vehicles
- manage integrations
- manage customers and bookings

------------------------------------------------
SUB ADMIN
------------------------------------------------

Delegated admin.

Can be restricted by station scope.

------------------------------------------------
WORKER
------------------------------------------------

Operational staff.

Permissions limited to operational modules.

------------------------------------------------
PRODUCT LICENSING INTERACTION
------------------------------------------------

Even if role allows access,
module access requires product enabled.

Example:

Org Admin
+ Rental enabled
= Rental access

------------------------------------------------
ACCESS EVALUATION ORDER
------------------------------------------------

1 authenticated
2 user active
3 resolve membership
4 check product enabled
5 check role permission
6 check station scope